
- How is a bulk request for a multitude of users is evaluated?
- what is the performance?

To Evaluate the permissions of many users at once you can formulate a json with all to be evaluated users and make a request

``` shell
# see the example with 10.000 users
"physical-access-control-opa/pip-info-employee-vde-trainings.json";

The evaluation happend in "0m 0s 64ms" on my relatively powerful machine.
``` 
